Welcome to IVAO Switzerland
 ATC Doc
¶


Do not forget to also view our website 
ivao.ch
.




Commands
¶




mkdocs new [dir-name]
 - Create a new project.


mkdocs serve
 - Start the live-reloading docs server.


mkdocs build
 - Build the documentation site.


mkdocs help
 - Print this help messageeeeeeeeeeeeeeeee.




Project layout
¶


mkdocs.yml    # The configuration file.
docs/
    index.md  # The documentation homepage.
    ...       # Other markdown pages, images and other files.
